parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Due to Piston Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the piston can cause the engine to seize or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver. This can also result in costly repairs, potentially exceeding $10,000.
symptoms: inability to restart the engine until it cools down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dynamic steering system can cause the steering wheel to become stiff or difficult to turn, making it challenging for the driver to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels stiff or difficult to turn
the steering wheel becomes heavy and hard to turn
the steering system offers intermittent or sporadic assistance
the vehicle displays a "Steering Defective" warning message
the steering wheel becomes stuck or unable to turn.

inability to trade-in or sell the vehicle due to unresolved recall issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Backup Camera Override by Phone Call
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The override of the backup camera screen by an incoming phone call can increase the risk of accidents or injuries while reversing, as the driver's visibility is compromised.
